name: Synex Renewable Energy Corporation
longDescription: Synex International Inc is an independent Canadian renewable power producer. It develops, acquires and operates renewable energy facilities. Synex International Inc generates revenue from three run of river power plants and one power line network in British Columbia. Synex is a renewable power developer with substantial wind and hydro projects under various levels of development in British Columbia.
